    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed and all achieved their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping for a Class II device with medium model influence. A known limitation exists in the output comparison factor: the CFD model over-predicts NIH by 31% at the low-flow high-speed edge condition. The team acknowledges this limitation. The overall credibility package is accepted as sufficient to support the COU decision. The risk associated with the edge-case over-prediction is considered acceptable.",
